rem  cygwin compiled make 3.81:           fails         fails?[7]
rem  mingw32 compiled make 3.79.1:        okay          okay
rem  mingw32 compiled make 3.80:          okay          okay?[7]
rem  mingw32 compiled make 3.81:          okay          okay[8]
rem
